articles.title: Australian PM Albanese to meet Xi Jinping in long-awaited China visit - BBC.com
articles.description: Anthony Albanese's trip - the first by an Australian leader since 2016 - follows years of strained ties.
articles.content:
Australian PM Anthony Albanese and Chinese President Xi Jinping have met for talks aimed at easing years of tensions in Beijing.
